if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('busi_order')
and type = 'U')
drop table busi_order
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: busi_order */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_order (
OrderID int identity(1,1),
OrderCode nvarchar(50) not null,
OrderMoney decimal(10,2) not null,
Count int not null,
Platform int not null,
ShopID int not null,
OpAdmin int null,
Status int null,
CountryID int null,
ImportTime datetime not null default getdate(),
IsDel bit not null default 0,
lasttime datetime null
)
go

if exists (select 1 from sys.extended_properties
where major_id = object_id('busi_order') and minor_id = 0)
begin

'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_order'

end

'业务-订单表(OK)',
